EN: He is drinking coffee.
ZH: 我喜欢喝茶而不是咖啡。
EN: I prefer to drink tea instead of coffee.
ZH: 爸爸晚上喝一杯啤酒。
EN: Dad has a beer in the evening.
ZH: 女儿喜欢喝果汁。
EN: The daughter likes to drink fruit juice.
ZH: 我们去饭馆喝啤酒吧。
EN: Let's go to a restaurant to have some beer.
ZH: 学生学习时最好不要喝咖啡。
EN: Students should not drink coffee while studying.
ZH: 明天我会喝一杯咖啡来提神。
EN: I will drink a cup of coffee tomorrow to refresh myself.
ZH: 他每天早上都喝牛奶。
EN: He drinks milk every morning.
ZH: 我想喝一杯冰水。
EN: I want to drink a glass of cold water.
ZH: 他一天可以喝好几瓶水。
EN: He can drink several bottles of water a day.
ZH: 女士不要喝太多酒。
EN: The lady should not drink too much alcohol.
ZH: 我们一定要喝足够的水。
EN: We must drink enough water.
ZH: 请给我来杯茶。
EN: Please give me a cup of tea.
ZH: 他不喜欢喝咖啡。
EN: He does not like to drink coffee.
ZH: 朋友们聚在一起喝庆祝。
EN: Friends gather together to drink and celebrate.
ZH: 你想和我一起喝杯酒吗？
EN: Do you want to have a drink with me?
ZH: 婚礼上客人们喝香槟庆祝。
EN: Guests drink champagne to celebrate at weddings.
